{"tid":2494264,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"193：仲有人用五虎呢個term咁娘咩？","createTime":"2021-04-18T13:28:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T14:51:42.000Z","uid":272565,"like":322,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"cbe0cefda5a4b2c4de1e9c4fe2615a05b4b2a43e","tid":2494264,"uid":272565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T13:28:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qme1LpjvUZ2LPEmWGEQu3dZwCm9tJgAAnSCLnWsFMS1MTR?filename=wrfajDW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwrfajDW.png&h=3144d0f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nERROR繼續只得3子現身，阿DEE曾發起網民投票行動，表示若得唱作人獎花姐就要穿低胸裝現身，193揚言由《全民造星》開始就想看花姐的「波罅」，希望他贏到。提到193最近人氣急升，升呢變「3爺」，兩位隊友笑言一向叫他「大爺」，193則謙稱想叫「3哥」因想代言米線店，他多謝大家支持，最開心帶挈ERROR孭飛的多個舊節目重新上架ViuTV，令更多觀眾睇到，他又自稱一向是娛樂圈清泉，即扮姜濤自稱處男鍾意食鮑魚，指花姐都有提他講說話就算部分正確也要禮貌些，澄清自己不小心用「老嘢」字眼，其實只想講老一輩。<br />\n對TVB出「千禧五虎」對撼，193再爆偉論：「而家仲有人用五虎呢個term咁娘咩？我哋而家係四隻白虎。」他又指相信講完之後有好多脫毛贊助，他直言怕得罪人，若有機會見到志偉哥也想跟他講對事不對人，自己沒說對方壞話，惟大家對號入座，自己一向尊重前輩。"},{"pid":"48a7330accee98ed7afacb6856e76cf0dcde67d2","tid":2494264,"uid":381968,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T13:28:40.000Z","msg":"3爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f82c215acc93622e2b6b9957969d46d6292aac51","tid":2494264,"uid":6604,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T13:29:06.000Z","msg":"Follower 又要爆升<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f76e352ff1f63c1926a649370b04c037461d613","tid":2494264,"uid":254453,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T13:30:10.000Z","msg":"知佢咩料啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da086a128997b8a95c2759496759270fe32c2a6e","tid":2494264,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T13:30:12.000Z","msg":"三爺<img